kpi_info.title: IUR_AVAILABILITY (M1004C143)
kpi_info.use: The number of samples when Iur interface is in working state. The Iu interface availability percentage can be calculated as a ratio of this counter and M1004C144. UPDATED:The counter is updated by value 1 once in approximately 10 seconds when the Iur interface SCCP subsystem is in working state.

kpi_info.title: IUR_AVAILABILITY_DENOM (M1004C144)
kpi_info.use: The number of samples for Iur availability measuring, used as a denominator for Iur availability percentage calculation. UPDATED:The counter is updated by value 1 once in approximately 10 seconds when the Iur interface exists in any state.

kpi_info.title: IUR_NOT_WORKING_DURATION (M1004C145)
kpi_info.use: The duration that Iur interface is in non-working state. UPDATED:Updated by the number of unavailability seconds when the Iur interface SCCP subsystem starts working after a break.

kpi_info.title: IUR_TO_WO_STATE_CHANGES (M1004C146)
kpi_info.use: The number of Iur interface state changes from non-working to working state. UPDATED:When the Iur interface SCCP sub-system state is changed to working state.
